INSERT INTO `about_pages` VALUES (1,'About Us','<p>Founded by Technologists for Future Technologists, the Center for Radiology Education represents far more than the opening of a new training facility, it marks the beginning of a movement, a promise, a commitment, and a family-driven mission to redefine how radiology students are educated, supported, and empowered as they enter or advance within the profession.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">This mission is personal, not just professional.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">The core focus of the Center for Radiology Education is to provide exceptional, hands-on education for students who are beginning their journey in medical imaging as well as those seeking to advance their clinical skills, confidence, and professional readiness. Beyond education, the Center is committed to creating meaningful pathways into the profession while raising awareness of the vital role radiologic technologists play in modern healthcare.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">For years, students in radiological sciences have had access to academic tutoring and theoretical instruction. But when students struggled clinically—when time at clinical sites was limited, hands-on opportunities were scarce, or confidence in positioning, patient care, and real-world workflow began to fade—there was nowhere to turn. That gap left many students overwhelmed, discouraged, and questioning whether they truly belonged in this profession.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">The Center for Radiology Education was built to change that narrative.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">Spanning 7,000 square feet, this one-of-a-kind facility was created with heart, intention, and an unwavering belief in the students who will one day care for our communities, our patients, and our families. It exists to provide what has long been missing in medical imaging education: real-world simulation, hands-on clinical practice, and the confidence that can only be built through experience—outside the pressure of the clinical environment.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">This is the first resource center of its kind, with plans to expand across the country—ensuring that no medical imaging student ever feels alone, unsupported, or unprepared again.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">In addition to supporting enrolled radiography students, the Center is dedicated to raising awareness of the profession at an early age by offering educational programs, summer camps, exposure opportunities, and hands-on experiences for students of all ages. By doing so, the Center helps cultivate interest, accessibility, and long-term growth within the radiologic sciences workforce.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\"><strong>Inside Our Training Centers</strong></p><ul><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">Seven fully equipped, fixed imaging suites</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">Mobile radiography units</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">C-arms for real-world procedural simulation</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">Ultrasound machines</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">PACS &amp; RIS systems</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">A modern classroom accommodating up to 50 students</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">A dedicated conference room for 20</p></li><li><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">Individual student workstations</p></li></ul><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">The Center for Radiology Education is an open-access resource, welcoming students from any school who need additional support, practice, mentorship, or career guidance. It was built for the student striving to grow, for the student chasing confidence, and for the student who simply needs someone to believe in them as strongly as they believe in their future.</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">At its core, the Center stands for one simple truth:</p><p dir=\"{&quot;dir&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\">When students are supported with exceptional education and meaningful pathways, patients win and the profession thrives.</p>','2025-12-28 10:52:08','2026-01-03 12:54:57');
